      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) for hemolysis index QoI must be below 5% on the fine grid.",
      "rationale": "Three-mesh study (3.2M, 8.7M, 22.1M cells) performed on the impeller passage. Richardson extrapolation yields GCI of 1.8% on the fine mesh for the hemolysis index, well within the 5% acceptance criterion. Achieved level 3 exceeds MRL 2 requirement of level 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
