      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions must match CFD inlet/outlet conditions within 5% for flow rate and rotational speed.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental data reports flow rates and rotational speeds with uncertainty bounds. CFD boundary conditions set to match nominal experimental values; deviations are within 2.3% for flow rate and 1.1% for rotational speed across all 5 operating points."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
